data.title: Gus Johnson (sportscaster)
data.meta_description: Augustus Cornelius Johnson Jr. is an American sportscaster. He is the lead play-by-play announcer for Fox Sports calling college football and college basketball. Prior to working with Fox, he was with CBS Sports. He also calls select NBA Playoff games for NBA on TNT and NBA TV.
